   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="Hs-30885,152_002"/><anchor type="textConst" xml:id="T_L02424-1"/><hi rend="pre-print">A. S.</hi><note type="textConst" corresp="T_L02424-1">ovaler Absenderkleber</note></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb68" type="place"><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="capitals">Wien, XVIII.</hi></hi></rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb168815" type="place"><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="capitals">Sternwartestr. 71</hi></hi></rs></addrLine></address><address><addrLine>Hrn Dr.</addrLine><addrLine>Hugo v. Hofma<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c>sthal</addrLine><addrLine><rs type="place" ref="#pmb173">Rodaun</rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb1006" type="place">Badgasse</rs>.</addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><pb facs="Hs-30885,152_001"/><rs ref="#pmb50" type="place">Wien</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><date>23. 12. 24</date></dateline></opener><p><salute>mein lieber Hugo,</salute> wollen Sie am <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L02424-1"/><date>31.</date>, <date>Mittwoch</date><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L02424-1"><ref target="1924-12-31" subtype="Cf" type="schnitzler-tagebuch"/>.
               </note>, letztem Tag d<damage agent="other"><supplied>es</supplied></damage> Monats u Jahres bei mir zu Mittag essen, und vorher, je nach Laune u
               Wetter, im freien oder geschlossenen Raume »plaudern«, <subst><del rend="overwritten">–<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/></del><add place="inline">(</add></subst>da ich doch beka<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c>tlich ein solcher bin –?) Ich
               würd <pb facs="Hs-30885,152_002"/>Sie circa <time>½ 12</time> erwarten. Schreiben Sie
               mir eine Zeile, ob ja. Herzlichst wie allezeit der Ihre</p><closer><signed>Arthur</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
